    <p align="justify">
        Reiki is a Universal life force energy which can be used to provide emotional and physical
        healing to the recipient either through hands on / hands off sessions. It is natural, non invasive
        healing therapy that works wonders at all most all levels. Although the main purpose of a Reiki
        Session is to bring about deep relaxation, It is also very effective in reducing pain ( both
        emotional and physical), helps one in identifying their “blocks” which prevents them to step up
        and helps in releasing those blocks thus giving a sense of “freedom” at all levels.
    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <br /><b> Things to know prior to the Session:</b> <br /><br />
        A Reiki Practitioner is attuned by a Master and so is deemed qualified to act as a medium to
