        off technique - which means the client will not be touched or asked to remove any clothing
        during the sessions. If a practitioner needs to use hands on technique then the client is
        informed and permission is taken before starting the session. There is no minimum or
        maximum time to allocate for a session, however a 45 minute session is recommended to fully
        experience this Energy.
    </p>
